node.text:
Circuit breaker day 23: Unagi don, with a side of miso soup for early lunch to coincide with gal's HBL schedule.

No japanese rice, never mind, I made up for it with flavoured jasmine rice (using seaweed mix). 👩‍🍳 Still tasted 👌

Happy mid-week and we can get over this together! Jiayou! 💪

#sgunited #circuitbreaker #stayhomesg
